			<title>Call for Peaceweek in Athens</title>
			<link>http://www.via.dds.nl/joomla2/index.php/nieuws-140/kamp-van-de-maand-mainmenu-120/290-pw-ath</link>
			<guid isPermaLink="true">http://www.via.dds.nl/joomla2/index.php/nieuws-140/kamp-van-de-maand-mainmenu-120/290-pw-ath</guid>
			<description><![CDATA[<div class="feed-description"><p><span>Call for the Peace next edition in Athens. </span><span style="line-height: 1.3em;">The Peace Week will consist of three different stages. First, the volunteers will participate in the Anti-Racism Festival of Athens, together with the team of SCI Hellas; then, pulling from our experiences in the festival and in our lives, we will create an artistic performance, combining theatrical parts with music, costumes or whatever fits our creativity, all together – a piece that speaks about peace, diversity, anti-discrimination and, ultimately, about humankind; to finish this work, we will present this itinerary work of art in the streets of Athens to sensitize people and spread the idea of peace.</span></p>
<p><span style="line-height: 1.3em;"><span>You can be one of the 14 participants from Netherlands that can participate in the peace weeks in Europe. 55% of the travel costs (up to 200 euro) as well as food and accommodation are covered.</span></span></p>
<p><span style="line-height: 1.3em;">Check it out all the </span>info at <a href="http://citizensbeyondwalls.org/agenda/peace-week-in-athens/"><span style="line-height: 1.3em;">http://citizensbeyondwalls.org/agenda/peace-week-in-athens/</span></a></p></div>]]></description>
