			<title>Peace week in Italy: `La città dell´utopia´</title>
			<link>http://www.via.dds.nl/joomla2/index.php/nieuws-140/kamp-van-de-maand-mainmenu-120/288-pw-italy</link>
			<guid isPermaLink="true">http://www.via.dds.nl/joomla2/index.php/nieuws-140/kamp-van-de-maand-mainmenu-120/288-pw-italy</guid>
			<description><![CDATA[<div class="feed-description"><p><span>“La Città dell’Utopia” (Utopia City- www.lacittadellutopia.it) is a project of SCI Italy that takes place in Rome. The project is an ongoing workshop on active citizenship and local development. There are different events, courses and workshops organized around 3 main themes: interculturality, sustainable lifestyles and active citizenship. “La Città dell’Utopia” will organize, together with social organisations in Rome, a public event connected with the european project “Citizens Beyond Walls” (see below) and one week workcamp called “Peace Week”. The public event will focus on Freedom of Movement, not only as a no border concept and the right to migrate, but also as a basic principle (a fundamental right) on which we claim human, social, civil and political rights within a Country.</span></p>
<p><span>How to apply?</span></p>
<p>Search<strong><span><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration: underline;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"> peace</span></span></span></span><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"> week</span></span></span><span style="background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"> </span></span></strong>in the browser of SCI home page (<a href="http://www.workcamps.info">www.workcamps.info</a>) and follow the instructions, or visit <a href="http://citizensbeyondwalls.org/agenda/peace-week-italy/">http://citizensbeyondwalls.org/agenda/peace-week-italy/</a></p></div>]]></description>
			<author>Rigasp@gmail.com (Rigas)</author>
