<div><span>There are still many vacant places for you motivated volunteers. Specially, Ramadhan Camp (IIWC 1414) and Tulungagung Camp (IIWC 1420) which is going to start on June 1st until 14th June 2014. This work camp is mainly organize an activities aimed to give volunteers experience on Indonesian Moslem Culture exposure, and support the orphans on the non-formal education field. There are also free place in August - September work camps.</span></div>
