			<title>Work protecting bears in Croatia!</title>
			<link>http://www.via.dds.nl/joomla2/index.php/nieuws-140/kamp-van-de-maand-mainmenu-120/271-kuterevo-workcamp-bear-sanctuary</link>
			<guid isPermaLink="true">http://www.via.dds.nl/joomla2/index.php/nieuws-140/kamp-van-de-maand-mainmenu-120/271-kuterevo-workcamp-bear-sanctuary</guid>
			<description><![CDATA[<div class="feed-description"><p>Join this wonderful project called L<span style="line-height: 1.3em;">and for the bears (Kuterevo, Croatia) which starts the 25 of may and will finish the 6 of jun.</span></p>
<p><span style="line-height: 1.3em;"> <img src="http://www.via.dds.nl/joomla2/via-media/content/camp-of-the-week/image.jpg" border="0" width="222" height="200" /></span></p>
<p><span style="line-height: 1.3em;"> </span><span style="line-height: 1.3em;">The workcamp will take place in the bear refuge of Kuterevo. The refuge is a local initiative that provide place for the orphaned bear cubs, to protect the bear habitat and to promote sustainable lifestyles and living tradition of the local mountains community which have coexisted with bears and wilderness for centuries.</span></p>
<div><span style="line-height: 1.3em;"> </span></div>
<div><span style="line-height: 1.3em;">What are you waiting for?</span></div>
<div><span style="line-height: 1.3em;"> </span></div>
<div><span style="line-height: 1.3em;">Check out all the info at:</span></div>
<div><span style="line-height: 1.3em;"> </span></div>
<div><span style="line-height: 1.3em;"> <span style="color: #0000ff;">http://kuterevo-bear-refuge.picnpin.com/</span></span></div>
<div><span style="line-height: 1.3em; color: #0000ff;"> http://kuterevo.wordpress.com/2014/03/06/workcamps-in-kuterevo-2014/</span></div>
